title: 800 Steps Express 5 Minute Fat Burner ‼️ Fat-burning Zone | Get fit FAST
description:
Running low on time like all of us? Only have time to squeeze 5 minutes of exercise in? #Celebs swear by this when traveling, and mums swear by this all the time - if you squeeze in a quick 5 minute session, you're 5 minutes closer to your goal. The key with this fat blasting workout is to go all in, because you will only get out what you put in to these sessions 💪 This session was designed to have you in your body's "fat-burning" zone in no time - which will optimise your session and melt away the pounds.

Smash this fun and fast-paced session out by itself, do it twice, or add on to one of my other workouts for a quick way to get your heart pumping. Whatever amount of time you have, make sure you make it count. Sweat it out and let's get #LIIT💥

channelDescription:
Welcome to my channel! My name's Gina B, an ex professional ballroom latin dancer turned fitness and nutrition coach based in Sydney, Australia! 

My goal is to help you take small STEPS (literally & figuratively) to create BIG changes in health and weight loss journey! Find joy through movement and boost your step count through a variety of FUN, music-led low impact and high impact workouts. 

So why should YOU join my YouTube channel community?

Consider me your virtual fitness bestie, cheering you on all the way to the end of the workout and beyond! I'll bring you new videos WEEKLY to keep you inspired, motivated, sane & entertained! 

Want extra accountability & support?

Join my private Facebook group: Upbeat Tribe! I'd love for you to become part of my female-focused community, a safe space where we can all support each other 💖
